{"title":"Beginner Projects Quick Reference Guide","html":"<h1 id=\"beginner-projects-quick-reference-guide\">Beginner Projects Quick Reference Guide</h1>\n<p>Quick reference for building ML projects.</p>\n<h2 id=\"table-of-contents\">Table of Contents</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#project-workflow\">Project Workflow</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#code-snippets\">Code Snippets</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#common-tasks\">Common Tasks</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#best-practices-checklist\">Best Practices Checklist</a></li>\n</ul>\n<hr />\n<h2 id=\"project-workflow\">Project Workflow</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>Problem Definition</li>\n<li>Data Collection</li>\n<li>EDA</li>\n<li>Preprocessing</li>\n<li>Model Training</li>\n<li>Evaluation</li>\n<li>Improvement</li>\n</ol>\n<hr />\n<h2 id=\"code-snippets\">Code Snippets</h2>\n<h3 id=\"load-data\">Load Data</h3>\n<pre class=\"shiki dark-plus\" style=\"background-color:#1E1E1E;color:#D4D4D4\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#D4D4D4\">df = pd.read_csv(</span><span style=\"color:#CE9178\">'data.csv'</span><span style=\"color:#D4D4D4\">)</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#DCDCAA\">print</span><span style=\"color:#D4D4D4\">(df.info())</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"></span></code></pre>\n<h3 id=\"handle-missing-values\">Handle Missing Values</h3>\n<pre class=\"shiki dark-plus\" style=\"background-color:#1E1E1E;color:#D4D4D4\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#D4D4D4\">df[</span><span style=\"color:#CE9178\">'column'</span><span style=\"color:#D4D4D4\">].fillna(df[</span><span style=\"color:#CE9178\">'column'</span><span style=\"color:#D4D4D4\">].median(), </span><span style=\"color:#9CDCFE\">inplace</span><span style=\"color:#D4D4D4\">=</span><span style=\"color:#569CD6\">True</span><span style=\"color:#D4D4D4\">)</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"></span></code></pre>\n<h3 id=\"train-model\">Train Model</h3>\n<pre class=\"shiki dark-plus\" style=\"background-color:#1E1E1E;color:#D4D4D4\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#C586C0\">from</span><span style=\"color:#D4D4D4\"> sklearn.ensemble </span><span style=\"color:#C586C0\">import</span><span style=\"color:#D4D4D4\"> RandomForestClassifier</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#D4D4D4\">model = RandomForestClassifier()</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#D4D4D4\">model.fit(X_train, y_train)</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#D4D4D4\">score = model.score(X_test, y_test)</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"></span></code></pre>\n<hr />\n<h2 id=\"common-tasks\">Common Tasks</h2>\n<h3 id=\"classification\">Classification</h3>\n<pre class=\"shiki dark-plus\" style=\"background-color:#1E1E1E;color:#D4D4D4\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#C586C0\">from</span><span style=\"color:#D4D4D4\"> sklearn.ensemble </span><span style=\"color:#C586C0\">import</span><span style=\"color:#D4D4D4\"> RandomForestClassifier</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#D4D4D4\">model = RandomForestClassifier()</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"></span></code></pre>\n<h3 id=\"regression\">Regression</h3>\n<pre class=\"shiki dark-plus\" style=\"background-color:#1E1E1E;color:#D4D4D4\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#C586C0\">from</span><span style=\"color:#D4D4D4\"> sklearn.linear_model </span><span style=\"color:#C586C0\">import</span><span style=\"color:#D4D4D4\"> LinearRegression</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#D4D4D4\">model = LinearRegression()</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"></span></code></pre>\n<hr />\n<h2 id=\"best-practices-checklist\">Best Practices Checklist</h2>\n<ul>\n<li> Do EDA first</li>\n<li> Handle missing values</li>\n<li> Encode categorical variables</li>\n<li> Split train/test properly</li>\n<li> Try multiple models</li>\n<li> Evaluate with appropriate metrics</li>\n<li> Document your work</li>\n</ul>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Remember</strong>: Start simple and iterate!</p>\n","source":"16-projects-beginner/projects-beginner-quick-reference.md","githubUrl":"https://github.com/NabidAlam/road-to-machine-learning/blob/main/16-projects-beginner/projects-beginner-quick-reference.md","module":"16-projects-beginner","lessonId":"projects-beginner-quick-reference","guideId":null,"type":"module"}